一免費坐狗鐵當罰咗"},{"pid":"422df8762e48955f4d4519ba90d68fd86b1dcad8","tid":1576701,"uid":132754,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T11:00:12.000Z","msg":"係咪唔記得咗紅磡站因爲沙中綫沉降...<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1576648\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1576648</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n上年8月，沙中線被揭發多個車站錄得沉降。而根據沙中線沉降監測點的報告中，沙中線共10個車站，除了何文田站及大圍站的沉降監測點未有錄得超標外，其餘涉及8個站，包括顯徑站、鑽石山站、啟德站、宋皇臺站、土瓜灣站、紅磡站"},{"pid":"6ab705169cd7760034bbd0de1e27fa4bf61b1dce","tid":1576701,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T11:02:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"54b436faa26ffcfe4811b64173db8be891e51b33","tid":1576701,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T11:03:02.000Z","msg":"唔係好多人捉人跳閂嘅咩<br />\n<br />\n做咩無人答我架"},{"pid":"0019fafddd52cc846a7a6970ad5a66cdb8a91538","tid":1576701,"uid":7516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T11:05:32.000Z","msg":"罰完再加你價都仲得呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88d6ffe6104c6480defa0725749376d4f09553fc","tid":1576701,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T11:06:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11116c1dffd7ddd0c40090f35673022b267bbafe","tid":1576701,"uid":93311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T11:09:06.000Z","msg":"左手比錢右手"},{"pid":"ba29b489c0e803878d9673b3742ad1b5d3fd9b48","tid":1576701,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T11:10:07.000Z","msg":"得閒無野做又壞<br />\n<br />\n阻人返工又阻人放工<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母垃圾黨鐵"},{"pid":"b76b579ba7eed50569bf60f3453d75abe35082cf","tid":1576701,"uid":211933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"11116c1dffd